###  http://w3id.org/dpp#hasComponent
<http://w3id.org/dpp#hasComponent> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                       rdfs:subPropertyOf <https://w3id.org/dppo/ontology/dpp-odp/hasPart> .


